item.description:
 &lt;p&gt;LAMP represents a full featured stack of the most popular web server, database, web programming language known as Apache, MySQL and PHP. This article will cover the steps on how to install the LAMP on a CentOS 6 and CentOS 7. &lt;/p&gt;
